---
import CardTitle from "../components/CardTitle.astro";
import MarketingLayout from "../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
import { getCompanyConfig } from "../lib/companyConfig";

const company = await getCompanyConfig(Astro.request);
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Services"
  description="Digital consulting, app & workflow development, full stack branding, SEO, managed hosting, and one-on-one training. 20+ years of real-world experience."
  label="What We Do"
  active="services"
>
  <section>
    <h2>Proven products and tactics that coalesce into results</h2>
    <p>
      Every engagement is tailored. Most clients come to us for a combination of the areas below.
      <a href="/contact">Tell us what you need</a> and we'll figure out the rest.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <CardTitle text="Development" />
        <p>
          We build websites with a style &amp; quality to match your brand perfectly. No prepackaged
          templates — a bespoke product with all the features you won't get from the $249 warehouses.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <CardTitle text="SEO / SEM" />
        <p>
          Our websites rank in search engines out of the box thanks to proper construction, uber fast
          hosting and near-perfect Lighthouse scores.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <CardTitle text="Workspace Email" />
        <p>
          A successful online presence means having a you@your-domain.com email. We set up Google
          Workspace for its cost-to-value ratio.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <CardTitle text="Brand Design" />
        <p>
          Update your current branding or start from scratch to refresh your look. We know how to
          make your business look professional without agency prices.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <CardTitle text="Custom Projects" />
        <p>
          Need a touchscreen virtual directory app for your event? A white-label ticketing solution?
          We've done it. If you can think it, we can build it.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <CardTitle text="Managed Hosting" />
        <p>
          The most important aspect of search engine visibility is reliable, fast hosting. We resell
          hosting from Kinsta Google Cloud servers.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Digital Consulting</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>20 years &amp; ~50 brand portfolios</li>
      <li>Optimization &amp; workflow streamlining</li>
      <li>UX/UI — what works for your brand</li>
      <li>A/B content &amp; design testing</li>
      <li>Professional design for your brand</li>
      <li>Mobile app development &amp; submission</li>
      <li>Domain acquisition &amp; social media configuration</li>
      <li>Content writing / sourcing &amp; review</li>
      <li>A network of partners to consult or hire</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>WordPress</h2>
    <p>Building on WordPress since v2.9.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Concise admins that make editing &amp; posting fun</li>
      <li>Designs that stand out without overdoing it</li>
      <li>WooCommerce &amp; Stripe configuration</li>
      <li>Strip out the bloat for speed &amp; stability</li>
      <li>SEMRush and Google Lighthouse compliance</li>
      <li>Proper action hooks and filters</li>
      <li>Coded to the repository codex standard</li>
      <li>Gutenberg Blocks on request or when appropriate</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Full Stack Branding</h2>
    <p>
      I've worked with almost 100 brands, learning how to follow proper identity guidelines. Get
      your brand recognized in all aspects of design and look like you spent a lot more.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Logos &amp; Icons / SVG</li>
      <li>HTML Email &amp; Newsletters</li>
      <li>Email Signatures</li>
      <li>Identity Manuals</li>
      <li>Sales Decks</li>
      <li>Landing Pages</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Training</h2>
    <p>
      One-on-one workshopping is truly the best way to learn a new skill or work through a bug you
      just can't find or fix.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Web Development — HTML, CSS, JS</li>
      <li>WordPress &amp; PHP</li>
      <li>Debugging</li>
      <li>Optimization &amp; Code Review</li>
      <li>Branding &amp; Content</li>
      <li>Search Optimization</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Minimal Plugins</h2>
    <p>
      A lot of website "developers" install plugins with reckless abandon — conflicting styles,
      higher chance of an update fail, and slower load times. 99% of the plugins I use for general
      tasks I have developed myself using the same code library.
    </p>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
